history.content: The Stevens Venture Center of Stevens Institute of Technology, a premier tech-focused institution in the New York metropolitan area, will be hosting a virtual COVID HealthHack II running from May 15-24th. This global hackathon is focused on the challenges presented to all of us as we move out of lockdown into the “new normal”. The new world post lockdown will require some novel solutions and approaches. Hack II was recently featured in Inc. Magazine and is awarding $5K in prizes. Please visit www.covidhealthhack.com to learn more!
